<p><a title="goto commit #2ab215b752" href="https://github.com/jquery/jquery-mobile/commit/2ab215b7522f853b0dbd2c3a72602227e81775a4">Moving to jQuery 1.8 as the default version</a><br />
- jQuery 1.8 (1.8.1) ist now the default version for jQuery Mobile 1.2.x</p>
